#. [message]: description=Malakar
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/10_Underground.cfg:333
msgid "Half-men. Where do these caves reach the surface?"
msgstr "Mezzi-uomini. Quale di queste gallerie porta alla superficie?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/10_Underground.cfg:337
msgid "Half...? Are you the blikkers who just smashed up the doorway?"
msgstr "Mezz...? Siete voi i balenghi che hanno appena distrutto il portone?"

#. [message]: description=Malakar
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/10_Underground.cfg:342
msgid "Many elves were in pursuit. We had no other choice."
msgstr "Molti elfi ci stavano inseguendo. Non avevamo altra scelta."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/10_Underground.cfg:346
msgid ""
"And you've brought elves in here with you? Gol, by the Beard. This is "
"nothing less than an invasion! Mobilize! Dwarven units, mobilize!"
