msgstr "Capitano Kogw! Capitano Kogw!"

#. [message]: description=Kogw
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/16_Exodus.cfg:141
msgid "Rhys?"
msgstr "Rhys?"

#. [message]: description=Kogw
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/scenarios/16_Exodus.cfg:146
msgid "You old scoundrel! How in blazes are you still alive?"
msgstr "Vecchio furfante! Come diavolo sei ancora vivo?"

