#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Caravel.cfg:6
msgid "female^Caravel"
msgstr "Caravella"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Caravel.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Caravels are medium-sized attack ships, armed with a ballista and a long-"
"range catapult."
msgstr ""
"Le caravelle sono navi da battaglia di taglia media, armate con una balista "
"e una catapulta a lunga portata."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Caravel.cfg:36
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Frigate.cfg:35
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Dreadnought.cfg:36
msgid "catapult"
msgstr "catapulta"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Clipper.cfg:5
msgid "female^Clipper"
msgstr "Clipper"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Clipper.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Clippers, although fast, are very weak. Armed with a ballista, they are used "
"primarily as scouts."
msgstr ""
"I clipper, anche se veloci, sono molto deboli. Armati di una balista, sono "
"usate principalmente per la ricognizione."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Dreadnought.cfg:5
msgid "female^Dreadnought"
msgstr "Corazzata"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Dreadnought.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Dreadnoughts are the pride of the humans' navy. With 3 ballistae and a "
"catapult, they can sink or kill almost anything unlucky enough to be in "
"their way."
msgstr ""
"Le corazzate sono l'orgoglio della marina degli uomini. Con tre baliste e "
"una catapulta, possono affondare o uccidere quasi qualsiasi cosa abbastanza "
"sfortunata da trovarsi sulla loro strada."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Frigate.cfg:5
msgid "female^Frigate"
msgstr "Fregata"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Frigate.cfg:22
msgid "The Frigate is rather slow, but it is powerful and well-protected."
msgstr "La fregata è piuttosto lenta, ma è potente e ben protetta."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Galleon.cfg:5
msgid "female^Galleon"
msgstr "Galeone"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Galleon.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Galleons are sailing warships. The humans' attempt at sea travel, they are "
"expensive, but very strong. Armed with three ballistae, they mete out "
"justice with deadly efficency."
msgstr ""
"I galeoni sono navi da guerra a vela. Sono il tentativo degli uomini di "
"viaggiare per mare, costosi ma molto potenti. Armate di tre baliste, "
"dispensano giustizia con efficienza mortale."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Cruiser.cfg:5
msgid "female^Pirate Cruiser"
msgstr "Incrociatore pirata"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Cruiser.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The Pirate Cruiser is a larger pirate ship, either built or captured. It has "
"3 ballistae."
msgstr ""
"L'incrociatore pirata è una grande nave pirata, costruita appositamente o "
"catturata. Ha tre baliste."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Galleon.cfg:5
msgid "female^Pirate Galleon"
msgstr "Galeone pirata"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Galleon.cfg:22
msgid ""
"The Pirate Galleon is a former battleship of the Wesnothian navy, captured "
"by renegades and pressed into service. It has 5 ballistae."
msgstr ""
"Il galeone pirata è una nave da guerra catturata alla marina di Wesnoth da "
"rinnegati e rimessa in servizio. Ha cinque baliste."

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Schooner.cfg:5
msgid "female^Pirate Schooner"
msgstr "Goletta pirata"

#. [unit]: race=boat
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/boats/Pirate_Schooner.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Pirates are the aquatic vector of Thieves. Manned by human renegades, these "
"widely feared ships ply the seaways, looking for plunder."
msgstr ""
"Le golette pirata sono i trasportatori acquatici dei ladri. Equipaggiate da "
"uomini rinnegati, queste navi solcano i mari alla ricerca di bottino."

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Cave.cfg:5
#, fuzzy
msgid "Cave Drake"
msgstr "Naga delle caverne"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Cave.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Those drakes that are born and raised in caves often suffer from stunted "
"growth and other deformations, as their internal fire never burns as "
"intensely as the fires of surface-dwellers. Although these drakes are frail "
"and weak aboveground, their small size makes them perfectly suited for "
"scouting caves ahead of the warriors of a tribe."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: race=drake
#. [unit]
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Chieftain.cfg:6
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/fake_units.cfg:11
msgid "Drake Chieftain"
msgstr "Drago capitano"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Chieftain.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Drake Chieftains are the leaders of their tribes. Skilled in the use of both "
"their sword and their internal fire, they are also trained from a young age "
"to lead their fellow Drakes into battle.\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
msgstr ""
"I draghi capitani sono i comandanti delle loro tribù. Esperti nell'uso della "
"spada e del loro fuoco interno, sono anche addestrati fin dalla giovane età "
"a guidare i loro compagni draghi in battaglia.\n"
"\n"
"Note speciali:"

