msgid "Drake Hatchling"
msgstr "Nidiata di drago"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Hatchling.cfg:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Newborn drakes, Hatchlings are used in times of desperation as cannon fodder "
"and cheap, scaly walls."
msgstr ""
"I draghi appena nati sono usati come carne da macello e sbarramento da poco."

