#. [unit]: race=drake
#. [unit]
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Lord.cfg:6
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/fake_units.cfg:29
msgid "Drake Lord"
msgstr "Signore dei draghi"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Lord.cfg:29
msgid ""
"A Drake Lord is the chieftain of a powerful and respected tribe. He wields a "
"sword doused in naphtha, against which few foes can stand. This, coupled "
"with his mastery of his internal fires, makes him an enemy few would dare to "
"fight.\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
msgstr ""
"Il signore dei draghi è il capitano di una tribù potente e rispettata. "
"Contro quei pochi nemici che possono affrontarlo, maneggia una spada bagnata "
"nel petrolio. Questa, abbinata al suo fuoco interno, lo rendono un nemico "
"che pochi oserebbero combattere.\n"
"\n"
"Note speciali:"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Lord.cfg:86
msgid "fire sword"
msgstr "spada di fuoco"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Magus.cfg:7
#, fuzzy
msgid "Drake Magus"
msgstr "Drago arcimago"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Magus.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The Drake Magi are fresh members of the Obsidian Citadel, who have been "
"bound to and mutilated by the cult. Although they have undergone training "
"harsh enough to kill any human or orc, they are inexperienced, and thus can "
"only safely wield a weaker form of their feared fireball spell. However, "
"they also share the weaknesses of the High Magi."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Priest.cfg:6
msgid "Drake Priest"
msgstr "Drago sacerdote"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Priest.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Their bodies marred by extreme torture and self-mutilation, the priests are "
"the spiritual leaders of the drakes, each one dedicated to a particular god. "
"However, their rituals have left them enfeebled, and unable to fly or "
"breathe fire.\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
msgstr ""
"Con i corpi segnati da drastiche torture e auto-mutilazioni, i sacerdoti "
"sono i capi spirituali dei draghi, ciascuno devoto a una specifica divinità. "
"Tuttavia, i loro rituali li hanno indeboliti e li hanno resi incapaci di "
"volare o soffiare fuoco.\n"
"\n"
"Note speciali:"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Slave.cfg:5
msgid "Drake Slave"
msgstr "Drago schiavo"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Slave.cfg:18
msgid "Drake Slaves are servile members of this reptilian race."
msgstr "I draghi schiavi sono membri servili di questa razza di rettili."

#. [variation]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Slave.cfg:77
msgid "Drake Rebel"
msgstr "Drago ribelle"

#. [variation]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Slave.cfg:92
msgid ""
"This was a drake slave, but it has grabbed a spear in rebellion against its "
"masters.\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
msgstr ""
"Questi era un drago schiavo, ma ha impugnato una lancia per ribellarsi ai "
"suoi padroni.\n"
"\n"
"Note speciali:"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Worker_Malakar.cfg:5
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Worker.cfg:5
msgid "Drake Worker"
msgstr "Drago lavoratore"

#. [unit]: race=drake
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Worker_Malakar.cfg:30
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/drakes/Worker.cfg:19
msgid "More advanced Drakes, the Workers fight with their maces."
msgstr "Draghi più avanzati, i lavoratori combattono con le mazze."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/nagas/Guardian.cfg:28
#: Flight_Freedom_1_3/units/nagas/Sentinel.cfg:29
